Bear in mind however, that these interfaces at the moment still have some limitations. They can *only* be displayed whilst having a message open, and the HTML formatting of the email may look a bit off. You can find more information on how to test &amp; run the code above by following [this link](https://developers.google.com/gsuite/add-ons/how-tos/testing-gmail-addons).


